import React from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import { Paper, TableContainer, Table, TableHead, TableRow, TableCell, TableBody, Typography, Container, Button } from '@material-ui/core' import { makeStyles } from '@material-ui/core/styles' const useStyles = makeStyles({ root: { background: 'linear-gradient(45deg, #FE6B8B 30%, #FF8E53 90%)', border: 0, borderRadius: 3, boxShadow: '0 3px 5px 2px rgba(255, 105, 135, .3)', color: 'white', height: 48, padding: '0 30px', }, }) const Users = ({ users }) => { const classes = useStyles() if (!users) { return null } return( Users User Blogs Created {users.map((user) => ( {user.name} {user.blogs.length} ))}
) } export default Users
